debates.showAs: All Terrain Vehicle Safety Bill 2018: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to regulate the safety standards of the composition of all terrain vehicles and to regulate health and safety practises in use of all terrain vehicles in the workplace.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do rialáil na gcaighdeán sábháilteachta a ghabhann le comhdhéanamh feithiclí uile-thír-raoin agus do rialáil cleachtais sláinte agus sábháilteachta i dtaca le húsáid feithiclí uile-thír-raoin san áit oibre.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Shábháilteacht Feithiclí Uile-Thír-Raoin,  2018

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to provide for the establishment of a body to be known as the National Infrastructure Commission to advise government on all sectors of economic infrastructure and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú maidir le comhlacht a bhunú ar a dtabharfar an Coimisiún um Bonneagar Náisiúnta chun comhairle a chur ar an rialtas maidir le hearnálacha uile an bhonneagair eacnamaíoch agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.

debates.showAs: Comptroller and Auditor General (Amendment) Bill 2017: Second Stage [Private Members]
Comptroller and Auditor General (Amendment) Bill 2017: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend the law relating to the Comptroller and Auditor General; to allow for certain supervisory powers in relation to infrastructure spending within the State; and to provide for related matters
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú an dlí a bhaineann leis an Ard-Reachtaire Cuntas agus Ciste; do cheadú cumhachtaí maoirseachta áirithe i ndáil le caiteachas ar bhonneagar laistigh den Stát; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara
bill.shortTitleGa: Bille an Ard-Reachtaire Cuntas agus Ciste (Leasú), 2017

debates.showAs: Assaults on Emergency Workers Bill 2012: Second Stage (Resumed)

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to revise the law relating to non-fatal offences against the person by imposing specific terms of imprisonment on persons found guilty of assaulting members of the emergency services whilst on duty
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht d'athmheas an dlí a bhaineann le cionta neamh-mharfacha in aghaidh an duine trí théarmaí sonracha príosúnachta a fhorchur ar dhaoine a chiontaítear i gcomhaltaí de na seirbhísí éigeandála a ionsaí le linn dóibh a bheith ar dualgas
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Ionsaithe ar Oibrithe Éigeandála 2012

debates.showAs: Landlord and Tenant (Business Leases Rent Review) Bill 2012: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to make provision for the prohibition of clauses within business leases which provide exclusively for the upward review of the rent payable under the lease and to ensure that all existing business leases may be reviewed in a manner that allows for the fixing of a rent which is less than, greater than or the same as the amount of the rent payable prior to the date on which the rent is reviewed
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú maidir le toirmeasc ar chlásail i léasanna gnó lena ndéantar socrú go heisiach le haghaidh athbhreithniú suas ar an gcíos is iníoctha faoin léas agus chun a chinntiú go bhféadfar gach  léas gnó láithreach a athbhreithniú ar mhodh lena gceadaítear cíos a shocrú is lú nó is mó ná, nó is ionann agus, méid an chíosa ab iníoctha roimh an dáta a athbhreithnítear an cíos
bill.shortTitleEn: Landlord and Tenant (Business Leases Rent Review) Bill 2012
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Thiarnaí Talún agus Tionóntaí (Athbhreithniú Cíosa Léasanna Gnó), 2012

debates.showAs: Spent Convictions Bill 2011: Referral to Select Committee

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to provide that certain convictions may be regarded as spent for certain purposes where the convicted person has not been convicted of any other offence within specified periods of years, and to provide for related matters
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú chun go bhféadfar a mheas gur ciontuithe spíonta chun críoch áirithe ciontuithe áirithe i gcás nár ciontaíodh an duine ciontaithe in aon chion eile laistigh de thréimhsí sonraithe blianta, agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara

debates.showAs: Electoral (Amendment) (Political Donations) Bill 2011: Order for Second Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to restrict the making of donations for political purposes by companies, trade unions, societies or building societies, to amend the law relating to the disclosure of donations to political parties and individuals, to provide for the auditing of the accounts of political parties and to implement the recommendations relating to political funding contained within the Second Report of the Tribunal of Inquiry into Payments to Politicians
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do chur srian le cuideachtaí, ceardchumainn, cumainn nó cumainn fhoirgníochta do thabhairt síntiús chun críoch polaitíochta, do leasú an dlí a bhaineann le síntiúis le páirtithe polaitíochta agus le pearsana aonair a nochtadh, do dhéanamh socrú maidir le cuntais páirtithe polaitíochta a iniúchadh agus do chur i ngníomh na moltaí a bhaineann le maoiniú polaitíochta atá sa Dara Tuarascáil ón mBinse Fiosrúcháin maidir le hÍocaíochtaí le Polaiteoirí
